text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha tampit khnhom chea mnoussa lok dauch puok anak der kreante ke ban phdal vea hi mk aoy khnhom tha pit brakd nasa mcheasa robsa puok anak kuchea mcheasa temuoyokt . dau che neah anaknea haey del sangkhumtha nung ban chuob mcheasa robsa ke chaur aoy ke sang ampeu na del la haey komaoy ke yk anaknea mneak thveuchea daikou knong karkorp sakkar champoh mcheasa robsa ke aoy saoh
